WEBVTT

00:00:01.290 --> 00:00:03.000
Yuzingizga qo'lingizni tekkizing.

00:00:03.496 --> 00:00:04.767
Qani sinab ko'ringchi.

00:00:05.586 --> 00:00:06.989
Nimani his qilyapsiz?

00:00:07.353 --> 00:00:09.236
Yumshoqmi? Mayinmi?

00:00:10.083 --> 00:00:12.693
Siz o'zingizni his qilyapsiz, 
shunday emasmi?

00:00:13.109 --> 00:00:14.812
Aslida esa unday emas.

00:00:15.387 --> 00:00:18.632
Siz barmoqlarizda va yuzlaringizda 
yashaydigan minglab mikroskopik

00:00:18.656 --> 00:00:21.197
mavjudodlarni his qilyapsiz.

00:00:22.481 --> 00:00:24.203
Siz bugun havo orqali kelgan mayda

00:00:24.203 --> 00:00:27.083
zamburug' moddalarni his qilyapsiz.

00:00:27.131 --> 00:00:29.098
Ular bizning allergiyamizni qo'zg'aydi

00:00:29.122 --> 00:00:30.674
va chrindi hidiga ega.